Package: TT
Title: Display tree structured data using datatable widget
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Michal",
           family = "Zielaskowski",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "michal.zielaskowski@gmail.com")
Description: Extension of datatable widget, allowing display of data.tree objects.
            All arguments of the data.tree become columns and each node is a row.
            Adds column with buttons allowing folding and unfolding the levels.
